name: Jamie Borthwick
summary: Jamie Borthwick, an actor known for his roles in "EastEnders," has made headlines with his recent participation in "Strictly Come Dancing." His success on "Strictly's Christmas special" has drawn attention, while critics have voiced concerns about his casting due to his lack of traditional ballroom dancing experience. The articles also address allegations of "cheating" raised by his fellow "Strictly" contestants. Despite these controversies, Borthwick remains a popular figure, with media outlets providing detailed profiles and insights into his life on and off the screen.
